---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Disclaimer from '../components/Disclaimer.astro';
---

<PageLayout
	title="About Antonio Rodríguez Martínez"
	description="Systems builder. Technical program manager. Father. I write, build, and create."
>
	<div class="space-y-4 md:space-y-6">
		<p class="animate-fade-up [animation-delay:0ms]">
			I build systems — digital, emotional, spiritual, and physical.
		</p>

		<p class="animate-fade-up [animation-delay:100ms]">
			I'm a technical program manager, software architect, and developer with over a decade of experience building scalable products. I've founded companies, led teams, and shipped software used by millions. Now I split my time between building tools and raising my kids.
		</p>

		<p class="animate-fade-up [animation-delay:200ms]">
			I'm also a father, artist, martial artist, mentor, and the founder of <strong class="text-text dark:text-text-dark theme-transition">Strong Hands, Soft Heart</strong> — a brand devoted to practical strength, emotional depth, and sacred self-reliance.
		</p>

		<p class="text-text dark:text-text-dark animate-fade-up [animation-delay:300ms] theme-transition">
			This blog documents raw reflections on:
		</p>

		<ul class="text-text dark:text-text-dark animate-fade-up [animation-delay:400ms] theme-transition">
			<li><strong class="text-text dark:text-text-dark theme-transition">Art & Expression</strong> 🎵 — creative soul, aesthetic power, truth-telling</li>
			<li><strong class="text-text dark:text-text-dark theme-transition">DIY & Creation</strong> 🛠️ — physical builds, handmade goods, crafting</li>
			<li><strong class="text-text dark:text-text-dark theme-transition">Integration & Growth</strong> 🧘🏽‍♂️ — inner mastery, parenting, masculine leadership</li>
			<li><strong class="text-text dark:text-text-dark theme-transition">Learning Projects</strong> 📚 — documentation of mastery in progress</li>
			<li><strong class="text-text dark:text-text-dark theme-transition">Metaspace</strong> 🌀 — reflections on the journey itself</li>
			<li><strong class="text-text dark:text-text-dark theme-transition">Parenting</strong> 👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 — raising resilient children, family dynamics, and personal growth</li>
			<li><strong class="text-text dark:text-text-dark theme-transition">Politics</strong> ⚖️ — power dynamics, social structures, and collective healing</li>
			<li><strong class="text-text dark:text-text-dark theme-transition">Psychology</strong> 🧠 — human behavior, social dynamics, and mental processes</li>
			<li><strong class="text-text dark:text-text-dark theme-transition">Systems & Strategy</strong> 💻 — technical systems, organizational design, and strategic thinking</li>
		</ul>

		<h2 class="text-text dark:text-text-dark animate-fade-up [animation-delay:500ms] theme-transition">👇 Links</h2>

		<ul class="text-text dark:text-text-dark animate-fade-up [animation-delay:600ms] theme-transition">
			<li>🛠 <a href="https://builds.software" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary-500 dark:text-primary-400 hover:underline theme-transition">Builds.software</a> — my technical portfolio</li>
			<li>💜 <a href="https://stronghandssoftheart.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary-500 dark:text-primary-400 hover:underline theme-transition">Strong Hands, Soft Heart</a> — my brand</li>
			<li>🐙 <a href="https://github.com/antoniwan" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary-500 dark:text-primary-400 hover:underline theme-transition">GitHub</a> — open source & code</li>
			<li>🌀 <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/antoniwan.online" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary-500 dark:text-primary-400 hover:underline theme-transition">BlueSky</a> — my social brain</li>
		</ul>

		<p class="text-text dark:text-text-dark animate-fade-up [animation-delay:700ms] theme-transition">
			For collaboration or questions, get in touch!
		</p>

		<div class="bg-background-alt/50 dark:bg-background-alt-dark/50 border-l-4 border-primary-500 dark:border-primary-400 p-element md:p-block my-block rounded-md shadow-sm theme-transition animate-fade-up [animation-delay:800ms]" role="complementary" aria-label="Disclaimer">
			<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
				<span class="text-xl" aria-hidden="true">🌟</span>
				<span class="font-semibold text-text dark:text-text-dark">Sacred Disclaimer</span>
			</div>
			<p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed m-0">The wisdom, practices, and digital alchemy shared here flow from personal experience and creative exploration. None of this constitutes medical, legal, psychological, or professional advice. Please consult qualified professionals for such guidance.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</PageLayout>